	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />整理行李的事终于告一段落了，<delay frames="40" />
这下可以放心地开始新生活啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果不是你在我搬来第一天就来看我，<delay20 />
我可能直到现在还会感到不安吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的很谢谢你！</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我终于把家里整理好了，<delay20 />
现在正在和<tag a="110" b="32" />上的大家打招呼。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很感谢你哦！<delay frames="40" />
很高兴你能在我搬来的第一天<delay20 />
就特意来看我～</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已经渐渐习惯了这里的生活，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />什么地方有什么东西也基本都记住了，<delay20 />
就算不看地图也没什么大问题了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没想到这里的生活挺方便的，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="32" />上的人也都很亲切，帮了我很多。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我打算这一周，<delay8 />我就在<tag a="110" b="32" />上到处走走，<delay20 />
熟悉一下这座里的事物。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还有很多不了解的地方，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以周围的一切都充满了新鲜感，<delay8 />
感觉非常有趣呢！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那个<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我今天找你，<delay20 />
除了要跟你问声好以外，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />还要送你一份礼物。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有东西想要给你，<delay frames="40" />
就当是<delay8 />我们相识的纪念吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />别客气，请收下吧！</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
在我之前住的<tag a="110" b="32" />非常有人气哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道你会不会喜欢，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不嫌弃的话，请用用看吧！</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
是从我的故乡买来的。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是广受好评的<delay8 />特产哦。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不介意的话，请用用看吧！</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="007_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />突然把你叫住，真是很抱歉呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后在这座<tag a="110" b="32" />很可能会有需要麻烦你的时候，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以还请多多关照！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那我就再打一下招呼，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今后请多多关照，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今后可能会有需要麻烦你的地方，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你有什么事需要我帮忙，<delay20 />
别客气，尽管跟我说！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
